-- title

Check For Section Flag Attribute


-- h2

Overview

Sections can have flag attributes
(e.g. `-- some-flag``). Templates
can check to see if a specific flag
exist for a section via:

-- code/

section_has_flag(
    section, 
    "target_flag_name"
)

-- /code


